OL,14,Fthe GL1 centre were given a ten
OL,15,Fpercent uplift in pay - at a time
OL,16,Fwhen the Aspire Leisure and Cultural
OL,17,FTrust, which ran the site, was
OL,18,F#500,000 in debt.
OL,20,FIt led to the trust suddenly closing
OL,21,Fthe leisure centre on 26 September.
